            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
                <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> amandes <supplied reason="lost">à coque tendre, tant; foin</supplied>, la charretée, 40 drachmes <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, vin 
                <supplied reason="lost">tant</supplied>; <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">raisin sous garantie, tant</supplied>; hors garantie, <supplied reason="lost">tant</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>; figues <supplied reason="lost">tant</supplied>; <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>; ail, le talent, 
                <supplied reason="lost">tant</supplied>; <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. <supplied reason="lost">Ressources totales de l'année, tant. Dépenses</supplied>
                des sacrifices <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> venant de l'édifice public <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> avec les serviteurs <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. Dépense totale de l'année 
                <supplied reason="lost">tant</supplied>. <supplied reason="lost">Reste</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>110 drachmes 2 oboles 1/2. <supplied reason="lost">Indemnité pour les démiurges, 3 mines</supplied>.</p>
