                for the sacrifices <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> from the public building <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> with the servants <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>. Total expense of the year 
                <supplied reason="lost">so much</supplied>. <supplied reason="lost">Remainder</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>110 drachmas 2 obols 1/2. <supplied reason="lost">Allowance for the damiergoi, 3 mines</supplied>.</p>
